    - target: {fileID: 8824057996292480126, guid: 3497b59561f014b4e8b99f0058019c72, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[0]'
      value: Look what the fucking cat dragged in. Supper.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8824057996292480126, guid: 3497b59561f014b4e8b99f0058019c72, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[1]'
      value: I am so fucking hungry right now and you're standing there with your
        little cunt ass looking like a whole meal...
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8824057996292480126, guid: 3497b59561f014b4e8b99f0058019c72, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[2]'
      value: Oh what, you think you're special? You're just some other run of the
        mill slop down here I get to munch on.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8824057996292480126, guid: 3497b59561f014b4e8b99f0058019c72, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[4]'
      value: 'You see that mountain behind me? And that beautiful, delectable maple
        boubon bbq whopper? '
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8824057996292480126, guid: 3497b59561f014b4e8b99f0058019c72, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[5]'
      value: If you don't want me to eat your legs right fucking now, you'd better
        find a way to roll that shit to the top.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8824057996292480126, guid: 3497b59561f014b4e8b99f0058019c72, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[6]'
      value: I used to eat those when I had to take my dumb chud kids to Burger King
        before I lost the custody battle.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8824057996292480126, guid: 3497b59561f014b4e8b99f0058019c72, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[7]'
      value: I'm not goin with you though, I've got elevators to take.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 8824057996292480126, guid: 3497b59561f014b4e8b99f0058019c72, type: 3}
      propertyPath: 'lines.Array.data[8]'
      value: Now, get me that JUICY rooftop view burger or I'm gonna ground your
        beef.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
